# Scissor Environment Variables

# 1. Clerk Authentication
# Create an application at https://clerk.com
# Copy the Publishable Key from the API Keys section
VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...

# 2. Convex Backend
# Create a project at https://convex.dev
# After running `npx convex dev`, your deployment URL will be generated
VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://...-....convex.cloud

# 3. Branded Short Domain
# Use this to display your own short-link domain instead of localhost during local development
VITE_SHORT_URL_BASE=https://scissor.link
